* George Perkins Clinton (1867-1937), an American botanist and mycologist;
* George Clinton (rugby league) (1924-2010), an English rugby league footballer who played in the 1940s and 1950s, and coached in the 1950s and 1960s.

Additionally, George Clinton Sweeney (1895-1966) was a United States federal judge.
